    "plan_content": "Here's a summary of the plan I researched and designed:\n\n---\n\n## Plan: Add PulseBoard Channel Plugin\n\n**7 new files**, all in `extensions/pulseboard/`. No existing files modified.\n\n### Key findings from codebase analysis\n\n| Finding | Detail |\n|---|---|\n| Best reference | `extensions/irc/` — medium-complexity, DMs + groups, exact same shape requested |\n| `getChatChannelMeta` source | Confirmed exported from `openclaw/plugin-sdk/core` at line 148 |\n| `createChatChannelPlugin` shape | `{ base: {...}, outbound?: {...} }` — `outbound` is a **separate top-level param**, not inside `base` |\n| `PluginRuntime` import | From `openclaw/plugin-sdk/core` directly (Telegram pattern; no local barrel needed for a fresh stub) |\n| Required `ChannelPlugin` cast | `as ChannelPlugin` needed in `index.ts` (IRC pattern) |\n| `getChatChannelMeta(\"pulseboard\")` | \"pulseboard\" isn't in the registry; cast the arg, then spread + override `label`/`docsPath`/`blurb` |\n\n### Files planned\n\n1. **`package.json`** — `@openclaw/pulseboard`, type module, openclaw block with `channel.id`, `channel.label`, `channel.selectionLabel`, `channel.docsPath`, `channel.blurb`\n2. **`openclaw.plugin.json`** — id/channels/configSchema with empty properties (mirrors IRC exactly)\n3. **`src/types.ts`** — `PulseBoardAccount`, `PulseBoardConfig`, `PulseBoardMessage`, + `ResolvedPulseBoardAccount` (needed by the generic constraint `TResolvedAccount extends { accountId?: string | null }`)\n4. **`src/runtime.ts`** — `createPluginRuntimeStore<PluginRuntime>` → exports `getPulseBoardRuntime` + `setPulseBoardRuntime` with error `\"PulseBoard runtime not initialized\"`\n5. **`src/channel.ts`** — `createChatChannelPlugin` with: meta (spread + override), capabilities (direct+group, no media), reload prefixes, config stubs, setup stubs, gateway log stub, `normalizeTarget` trimmer, and outbound adapter (deliveryMode/textChunkLimit/sendText returning `{channel, to, messageId}`)\n6. **`index.ts`** — `defineChannelPluginEntry` with id/name/description/plugin/setRuntime\n7. **`setup-entry.ts`** — `defineSetupPluginEntry(pulseBoardPlugin)`",
